but I can knock off 5% from the $69.99.

23:07.437 --> 23:09.564
The shoes were just marked down
from $155,

23:09.673 --> 23:15.236
so you're looking at $1,042.68.

23:18.448 --> 23:20.712
I'm pretty good with numbers.

23:21.918 --> 23:24.045
- Yeah.
- I guess so.

23:24.154 --> 23:26.452
