when I can ring that up for you guys.

23:26.556 --> 23:27.691
- Yes. Thank you.
- Thanks.

23:27.691 --> 23:28.453
- Yes. Thank you.
- Thanks.

23:33.764 --> 23:34.788
Hey.

23:37.567 --> 23:38.590
Hey.

23:39.835 --> 23:42.736
- Could you help me?
- Oh, yeah. Yeah, sure.

23:43.539 --> 23:45.871
